<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TRAFFIX MX – Verifica tu correo</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Exo+2:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/components/navbar.css">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { min-height: 100vh; background: #0a0a0a; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
               display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
        .bg-layer {
            position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% 40%, rgba(245,197,24,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }
        .scanlines {
            position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 1; pointer-events: none;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(to bottom,
                transparent 0px, transparent 3px, rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 3px, rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 4px);
        }
        .page-wrapper {
            flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            padding: 60px 20px; position: relative; z-index: 2;
        }
        .card-panel {
            width: 100%; max-width: 500px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(245,197,24,0.25);
            border-radius: 16px; padding: 56px 44px; backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            text-align: center; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
        }
        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(24px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
        }
        .icon { font-size: 56px; margin-bottom: 24px; animation: pulse 2s ease infinite; }
        @keyframes pulse { 0%,100% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { transform: scale(1.08); } }
        .badge-tag {
            display: inline-block; font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif; font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 3px; color: #f5c518;
            background: rgba(245,197,24,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(245,197,24,0.3);
            padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        h2 { font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800;
             color: #fff; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.2; }
        h2 em { color: #f5c518; font-style: normal; }
        .desc { color: #888; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 36px; }
        .desc strong { color: #ccc; }
        .divider { height: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); margin: 32px 0; }
        .steps { text-align: left; }
        .step { display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .step-num {
            flex-shrink: 0; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(245,197,24,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(245,197,24,0.4);
            color: #f5c518; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        }
        .step-text { color: #aaa; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; padding-top: 4px; }
        .btn-login {
            display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; padding: 14px 36px;
            background: #f5c518; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
            font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 2px; border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
        }
        .btn-login:hover {
            background: #ffd740; color: #0a0a0a; transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(245,197,24,0.3);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-custom">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a href="/" style="background-image:url(/images/home/logo.png);background-size:contain;background-repeat:no-repeat;width:100px;height:100px;"></a>
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">TRAFFIX MX</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="bg-layer"></div>
    <div class="scanlines"></div>

    <div class="page-wrapper">
        <div class="card-panel">
            <div class="icon">📧</div>
            <div class="badge-tag">TRAFFIX MX</div>
            <h2>Revisa tu<br><em>correo</em></h2>
            <p class="desc">
                Te enviamos un enlace de verificación.<br>
                <strong>Tienes 24 horas para activar tu cuenta.</strong>
            </p>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-num">1</div>
                    <div class="step-text">Abre tu bandeja de entrada y busca un correo de <strong style="color:#f5c518">TRAFFIX MX</strong>.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-num">2</div>
                    <div class="step-text">Haz clic en el botón <strong style="color:#f5c518">"Verificar mi correo"</strong>.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-num">3</div>
                    <div class="step-text">Una vez verificado, podrás iniciar sesión normalmente.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-num">4</div>
                    <div class="step-text">¿No lo ves? Revisa tu carpeta de <strong style="color:#ccc">spam o correo no deseado</strong>.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="divider"></div>
            <a href="/login" class="btn-login">IR AL INICIO DE SESIÓN</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/navbar.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
